    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159170/extras/51fbfdeac1885a2c3ee683960a0cb1f2.avif?t=1771765425\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Light Fairytale</strong> is a turn-based Japanese-style RPG series set in a dying underground world ruled by an evil empire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the golden age of '90s JRPGs, the series blends classic design with modern visuals and quality-of-life features.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Episode 3</strong> continues after Haru's encounter with the mysterious girl. As the truth behind the 'Sky' begins to unfold, he gathers a party of new and familiar faces and embarks on a journey filled with twists, secrets, and emotional moments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159170/extras/f9188466b72291c594a5b33310cffe59.poster.avif?t=1771765425\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159170/extras/f9188466b72291c594a5b33310cffe59.webm?t=1771765425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159170/extras/f9188466b72291c594a5b33310cffe59.mp4?t=1771765425\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic turn-based battles directly on the field.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modern real-time 3D visuals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute chibi-style characters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand-crafted anime cutscenes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >English, French, and Japanese support.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ultra-wide and stereoscopic 3D support.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Characters</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159170/extras/b9e1305f6fcf7db42703c8329d59da6c.avif?t=1771765425\" width=1560 height=652 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hikari</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cryptic, silver-haired girl with sharp words and fierce resolve, hiding a fragile heart.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159170/extras/a9cb29b7341d2a6e00fa8bd121b0db2a.avif?t=1771765425\" width=1560 height=628 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Emiko</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A striking woman with a charming smile and an unhealthy love for money.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beneath her greed lies a painful past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159170/extras/24098d674257b16aefd70cc34a15b281.avif?t=1771765425\" width=1560 height=628 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>About the 'Light Fairytale' series</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each episode is a standalone game. Episode 3 offers 4 to 8 hours of gameplay at normal difficulty and speed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optionally, import your clear save from previous episodes to carry over stats, items, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159170/extras/5f948a000f5adacd44307f5f2ad5d280.avif?t=1771765425\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>",
